67002" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=1764036&amp;issue-id=140795&amp;journal-id=440&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=The+Lancet&amp;title=Transmission+of+infectious+diseases+during+commercial+air+travel.&amp;author=A+Mangili&amp;author=MA+Gendreau&amp;volume=365&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;pages=989-996&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1764036&amp;issue-id=140795&amp;journal-id=440&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="pone.0000143-Hayden1">19. <span class="element-citation">Hayden FG, Treanor JJ, Fritz RS, Lobo M, Betts RF, et al.  Use of the oral neuraminidase inhibitor oseltamivir in experimental human influenza. <span><span class="ref-journal">Journal of the American Medical Association. </span>1999;<span class="ref-vol">282</span>:1240\xe2\x80\x931246.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/10517426" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=1764036&amp;issue-id=140795&amp;journal-id=440&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Journal+of+the+American+Medical+Association&amp;title=Use+of+the+oral+neuraminidase+inhibitor+oseltamivir+in+experimental+human+influenza.&amp;author=FG+Hayden&amp;author=JJ+Treanor&amp;author=RS+Fritz&amp;author=M+Lobo&amp;author=RF+Betts&amp;volume=282&amp;publication_year=1999&amp;pages=1240-1246&amp;pmid=10517426&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1764036&amp;issue-id=140795&amp;journal-id=440&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div></div></div></div><!--post-content--><div class="courtesy-note whole_rhythm small"><hr />Articles